==English==

===Etymology===
Coined by [[w:L. Ron Hubbard|L. Ron Hubbard]], probably from [[turbulent]] or [[disturbed]].

===Verb===
{{en-verb|enturbulat|es}}

# (''non-standard'') To [[agitate]] or [[disturb]]; to [[upset]], [[harass]].

===Usage Note===
This word is a [[shibboleth]] used almost exclusively by members or former members of Scientology.

